Title: An Act Changing the Name of Barangay Guinsampanan in the Municipality of Dumangas, Province of Iloilo, to Barangay Monfort Sur
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 690
An Act Changing the Name of Barangay Guinsampanan in the Municipality of Dumangas, Province of Iloilo, to Barangay Monfort Sur
Section 1. The name of Barangay Guinsampanan in the Municipality of Dumangas, Province of Iloilo, is changed to Barangay Monfort Sur.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: March 7, 1984
